# Workspace sandbox scopes

When `git branch --show-current` matches `sandbox/*`:

1. Read [.cursor/workspace-scopes/](../workspace-scopes/) for the active branch
2. Follow the matching scope skill (`glucose-for-watch-*-scope`)
3. **Refuse** edits outside allowed paths — route fixes to the owning sandbox or `feat/bloc-*` on `develop/integration`
4. Before commit: `glucose-for-watch-repo-hygiene` (no secrets, no `local.properties`, no real glucose in docs/qa)
5. PR to `develop/integration`: CI green + `glucose-for-watch-pr-gatekeeper`

Post v0.6.0: **`sandbox/mobile-app`** and **`sandbox/documentation`** primary; rebase sandboxes weekly on `develop/integration`.

See [docs/plan/WORKSPACE.md](../../docs/plan/WORKSPACE.md).
